    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Culture and style related to Kuva (Quva), now in Uzbekistan, which was a medieval hub of culture and art. Style is particularly associated with pottery, jewelry, and metalwork.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
